<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.9.1">
<l>vaṭṭu naṭuvē vaḷarkiṉṟa māṇikka</l>
<l>moṭṭu nuṉaiyil muḷaikkiṉṟa muttēpōl</l>
<l>coṭṭuc coṭṭeṉṉat tuḷikkat tuḷikkaveṉ</l>
<l>kuṭṭaṉvan teṉṉaip puṟampulkuvāṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvinta ṉeṉṉaip puṟampulkuvāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My little one, coming while droplets drip</l>
<l>like pearls that appear from the tip</l>
<l>of [His] ruby [red] penis</l>
<l>that grows between [two] balls,</l>
<l>will embrace me [from] behind;</l>
<l>Govinda will embrace me [from] behind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
